THE RECESSION and special charges reduced George Weston's second-quarter
profit by about 90 per cent.
The Weston family's main Canadian holding company earned CDollars 3.8m
(USDollars 3.22m) or 3 cents a share, down from CDollars 51.3m or CDollars
