FT  07 AUG 92 / World News in Brief: Mystery Aids symptoms
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Nine more patients have been reported as having Aids symptoms but no
infection with the Aids virus, the US Centres of Disease Control said. Most
of the 14 such cases have no risk factors for HIV.
