FT  07 AUG 92 / World News in Brief: Royal Navy chases suspect
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Roderick Newall, accused of murdering his parents in Jersey in 1987,
appeared in court in Gibraltar after a dramatic arrest at sea. A Royal Navy
frigate stopped him aboard a yacht 150 miles off Gibraltar. He is in custody
pending extradition proceedings.
